n o t e s

Over the past 15 years, literally thousands of the
world's most iconic DJs, producers and live acts
have mesmerized audiences with awe-inspiring sets
at Ultra events in Argentina, Brazil, Chile,
Croatia, Ibiza, South Korea and of course Miami.

In 2015, Ultra Music Festival continues to push the
boundaries, bringing an unparalleled combination of
cutting edge production and the world's best EDM
acts to new frontiers. Ultra Records is proud to
release the official Ultra Music Festival album.
This compilation includes the biggest names in
dance music from Flosstradamus, Blasterjaxx, Steve
Aoki, Kygo and more.
